        <div class="modal-content">
            <button id="closeUploadModalButton" class="modal-close">âœ–</button>
            <div style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                Subite unas fotis, Rey ðŸ‘‘ <span style="font-size: 0.85em;">(mÃ¡ximo 5)</span>.
